A BITE OF CHINA
When we see the movie Chinese food is praised by
the people. Recently there is a famous movie called
A Bite of China the movie is popular it introduces
Chinese food from different places. The audience is
attracted by the delicious food they never thought
Chinese food would be So various

FRUITS SALAD
First; prepare fruits, get ready a bowl; a teaspoon and
cup; and have salad cream; sugar, salt, honey and
yogurt: Then let our work begin. wash all the fruit and
peel the apples; pears and bananas, cut the
watermelon and put them all in a bowl and we need
to add the sources and mix them even. Finally; &
beautiful fruit salad is complete
